ans are from 2025-06-07 19:00:30, indicating cartservice pods likely crashed at the start of the anomaly window, causing client timeouts and connection failures.",\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_pod_status_at_timestamp",\n    "reason": "Server spans completely missing during fault period indicates service unavailability/crash",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["pod_processes", "pod_restart_count", "container_memory_usage"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["cartservice", "OOMKilled", "exit", "crash", "panic"],\n    "critical_timestamp": "2025-06-08 03:10:21"\n  }\n}\n```'}
